<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><!DOCTYPE article  PUBLIC '-//OASIS//DTD DocBook XML V4.4//EN'  'http://www.docbook.org/xml/4.4/docbookx.dtd'><article><articleinfo><title>BuildFarm/OpenBsdInstall</title><revhistory><revision><revnumber>8</revnumber><date>2021-10-24 22:10:53</date><authorinitials>FrancescoChemolli</authorinitials></revision><revision><revnumber>7</revnumber><date>2021-06-22 22:18:14</date><authorinitials>FrancescoChemolli</authorinitials><revremark>updated</revremark></revision><revision><revnumber>6</revnumber><date>2013-10-21 21:16:50</date><authorinitials>FrancescoChemolli</authorinitials><revremark>updated some informations</revremark></revision><revision><revnumber>5</revnumber><date>2012-06-19 15:20:54</date><authorinitials>FrancescoChemolli</authorinitials><revremark>fixed package installation instructions</revremark></revision><revision><revnumber>4</revnumber><date>2011-05-11 16:57:14</date><authorinitials>FrancescoChemolli</authorinitials><revremark>added power management info</revremark></revision><revision><revnumber>3</revnumber><date>2011-04-22 21:43:33</date><authorinitials>FrancescoChemolli</authorinitials><revremark>clarified some info about autoconf and automake versions</revremark></revision><revision><revnumber>2</revnumber><date>2011-04-22 15:40:45</date><authorinitials>FrancescoChemolli</authorinitials><revremark>fixed macro</revremark></revision><revision><revnumber>1</revnumber><date>2011-04-22 11:50:56</date><authorinitials>FrancescoChemolli</authorinitials></revision></revhistory></articleinfo><section><title>System Setup</title><orderedlist numeration="arabic"><listitem><para>create jenkins user <code>useradd -m jenkins; passwd jenkins</code> </para></listitem><listitem><para>set PKG_PATH in /root/.profile (e.g. to <code>ftp://mirror.switch.ch/pub/OpenBSD/`uname -r`/packages/`machine -a`</code> </para></listitem><listitem><para>add packages: <code>pkg_add jre git cppunit libxml ccache autoconf automake libtool m4 bash</code> </para><itemizedlist><listitem override="none"><para>autoconf and automake will likely require to resolve a conflict in version numbers; choose the most appropriate one and iterate for them </para></listitem></itemizedlist></listitem><listitem><para>you may want to also add <code>pkg_add vim</code> </para></listitem><listitem><para>enable power management (for automatic system shutdown) </para><itemizedlist><listitem override="none"><para>in <code>/etc/rc.conf.local</code> set <code>apmd_flags=&quot;&quot;</code> </para></listitem></itemizedlist></listitem></orderedlist></section><section><title>Build instructions</title><itemizedlist><listitem><para>make sure to set up the environment variables <code>AUTOMAKE_VERSION</code> and <code>AUTOCONF_VERSION</code> </para></listitem></itemizedlist></section></article>